by linaori at 2019-08-17T19:52:41Z

From a DX perspective, this would be really amazing if we could make something like this:

```yaml
# config/routes.yaml
doc_shortcut:
    path: /doc
    controller: RedirectController
    defaults:
        route: 'doc_page'

legacy_doc:
    path: /legacy/doc
    controller: RedirectController
    defaults:
        path: 'https://legacy.example.com/doc'
```
Or perhaps:
```yaml
# config/routes.yaml
doc_shortcut:
    path: /doc
    redirect:
        route: 'doc_page'

legacy_doc:
    path: /legacy/doc
    redirect:
        path: 'https://legacy.example.com/doc'
```
